{"tid":1157684,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"上得多連登令我講嘢同諗嘢變得好無營養","createTime":"2019-05-16T12:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T07:45:47.000Z","uid":131262,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3db5967753e76de304a6dd44f8312b2a926f005e","tid":1157684,"uid":131262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T12:45:27.000Z","msg":"話說而家返緊間公司，同好多後生嘅同事都傾得好埋，因為同同輩講嘢好多時八卦下，講下戇鳩嘢又一日。<br />\n<br />\n但今日老細約咗我食午飯，自然要同佢講返相對有營養嘅說話，語氣更加要得體。噉佢一路keep住同我講嘢，但我就完全諗唔到嘢同佢講，只係諗到平時連登啲膠嘢。直到佢問我「你知唔知點解我會調你去依個部門？」佢一問問題，我就抑壓唔到自己嘅衝動，自信滿滿大聲噉答：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「答案係陳國邦括弧李斯！！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當刻時間彷彿停止流動，老細定咗格幾秒之後就繼續食飯，無再同我講嘢。我終於醒覺，我已經成為咗不折不扣嘅連登仔。有無人可以教我點先可以回復正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eac6a4c6c29e12dc76fcae109c2aa230e3f26c1","tid":1157684,"uid":136038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"善"},{"pid":"55b4d6cacae115c4d7fe6528e42d249f6414ddb4","tid":1157684,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f60b0dbfcbfff96c349ba1aebda4e4f072a079e","tid":1157684,"uid":146376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"55b4d6cacae115c4d7fe6528e42d249f6414ddb4","tid":1157684,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5eac6a4c6c29e12dc76fcae109c2aa230e3f26c1","tid":1157684,"uid":136038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"善"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"打"},{"pid":"eb353f7e713a7a5525d991ec19e87234426df58b","tid":1157684,"uid":253277,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9be29ea1cc3670a4cd2f21a9dba31a7636d0cd8d","tid":115768